Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but that glass is just so thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:45.90,jp.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめん　そこのガラス厚くてさぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to speak up\Nwhen you talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.71,jp.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大きな声で話してくれないと聞こえないのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got serious trouble, Acting Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:56.49,jp.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,代行　たいへんです
